<div class="prose-content max-w-3xl">

  <p>We welcome new patients who live within our practice area. Registration is free and available to everyone who is entitled to NHS care.</p>

  <h2>Before you register</h2>
  <p>Please check that your home address is within our <a href="/new-patients/practice-area/">practice catchment area</a>. If you're not sure, call us on <a href="tel:{{ site.phone | replace(' ', '') }}">{{ site.phone }}</a> and we'll let you know.</p>

  <h2>How to register</h2>
  <ol>
    <li>
      <strong>Download and complete the registration form</strong><br>
      You can download a registration form from the link below, or pick one up from our reception at Cameron Health Centre.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>Return the completed form to us</strong><br>
      Drop it in to our reception, or post it to us at Cameron Health Centre, Methil, Leven, KY8 3LG.
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>We'll confirm your registration</strong><br>
      Once we've processed your form, we'll be in touch to confirm you're registered. This usually takes a few working days.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <a href="#" class="btn btn--primary inline-flex mb-6">
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
